author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 360
acceptance_criteria: "Governance automation roadmap includes deterministic normalization/reporting capabilities, validation checks for low-signal metadata, and safe operational workflows that reduce manual force-override churn while preserving ownership semantics."
definition_of_ready: Existing governance baseline metrics and pain points are documented from recent tracker sweep.
goal: Governance operations by default
objective: Replace manual sweeps with repeatable command-level workflows
value: Cuts governance maintenance cost and improves consistency
impact: Reduces manual mutation risk and accelerates future tracker cleanup
outcome: Future agents can run governance upkeep through supported pm surfaces
why_now: Current standards-alignment required long scripted passes and ownership remediations that should be converted into productized workflows.
reviewer: maintainer-review
risk: medium
confidence: medium
